name: Kevin Van Ausdal
message: We will take that fight to Congress. Have a Dept of Labor that works for us and for good businesses that follow the rules. We need teachers that get paid fairly, blue collar jobs that you can raise a family on, support the trades, and ensure we keep the promise we won with blood.

name: Kevin Van Ausdal
message:
So Labor Day is about remembering that we don't have to let ourselves be forced to work off the clock, to take work home, to accept harassment or unsafe conditions. We can stand up. We can say no.

We are Americans, we have the right not be abused on the job and earn an honest $

message:
We all know the grocery bill has gotten brutal and we look for creative ways to make budgets work. Even before Covid hit we lived that and now we face new challenges.

In NW GA our people are worried about keeping the job they have because finding a new one is much harder.

name: Kevin Van Ausdal
message:
Hopefully you all got to enjoy the holiday, but we want to dig into why Labor Day is so important right now.

The stock market keeps going up but our wages don't. Our productivity is higher than ever but our quality of life isn't matching it...

name: Kevin Van Ausdal
message: We have nothing we didn't fight for. Workers' rights. Civil rights. Women's rights. LGBT rights. Even our nation was birthed from a Revolution against unequal representation.
